**16.** The Patriarch elected that the alimentary canal be utilized to convert sinful creatures- namely sheep and cattle- into components utilized in the reconstruction of MEKHANE. 
**17.** Before the collapse of Amoni, a schism within the Patriarchy would cause the stomach to be ruined and forgotten.
