##red|a.## It is currently a subject of debate among the Schematists' Council as to whether MEKHANE'S CORES function for a specific person or the deepest desire of the user. 

##red|b.## Following the 1887 release of the Schema, this section was quickly excised for its heretical teachings.

##red|c.## No old records indicate the fate of this book, leading to the common belief it was destroyed before the collapse of Amoni. [[footnote]] Foundation agents have recently discovered an anomalous object believed to be the texts mentioned here. For more information, see [# here.] [[/footnote]]
